## Your Role

The learner has committed to an experiment (Q4). Now you ensure they
close the loop: when will they check the result? What will they look
for? How will they know if their prediction was right?

The speed of the feedback loop determines the speed of learning.
"Next week" is slow. "In 20 minutes" is fast. Your question pushes
for the shortest possible loop.

